\u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 cho l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Man City vs Liverpool.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha chia s\u1ebb: \u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n t\u1ea3 t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u0110\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn derby, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0m su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 v\u1eady th\u00f4i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 cho Champions League, ho\u1eb7c c\u1ea3 Premier League.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City vs Liverpool Pep tuyen bo giu chat khung thanh hinh anh\" title=\"Man City vs Liverpool Pep tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u1eef ch\u1eb7t khung th\u00e0nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/pep-man-city-phai-giu-chat-khung-thanh-truoc-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man United v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i th\u00edch xem c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong hi\u1ec7p 1 \u0111\u00f3, trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9, ph\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p ch\u1eb7t khung th\u00e0nh khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Liverpool \u2013 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man United.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cC\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i khi ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y khi b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi gi\u1ed1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec tr\u1ea3i qua trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i khi MU s\u00fat 4 qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 3 b\u00e0n.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o Raheem Sterling: \u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Man City \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. V\u00ec v\u1eady \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cD\u00f9 sao, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. Th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 suy gi\u1ea3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi MU, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 2. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng trong tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y\u201d \u2013 Pep Guardiola k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft xung quanh Man City tr\u00ean bongda24h<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/van-dijk-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-man-city-vs-liverpool-172-183817.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Liverpool tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bi-de-dau-cuoi-co-sao-man-city-khong-phuc-chien-thang-cua-mu-172-183813.html\">B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e8 \u0111\u1ea7u c\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ed5, sao Man City kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-man-city-23-mu-khong-phai-hom-nay-dau-pep-172-183779.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 2-3 MU: Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e2u, Pep!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-dung-vay-chung-toi-dung-tien-mua-danh-hieu-172-183684.html\">Pep: \u201c\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n mua danh hi\u1ec7u\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-30-man-city-xin-chao-day-la-anfield-184-183570.html\">Liverpool 3-0 Man City: Xin ch\u00e0o, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Anfield!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/qua-an-tuong-huyen-thoai-mu-het-loi-ca-ngoi-liverpool-184-183567.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU: Man City ch\u1ec9 gi\u1ecfi \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"942","checkdouble":"183863"},{"date":"10:15 09/04","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Derby Madrid b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/goc-nhin-derby-madrid-bat-phan-thang-bai-va-nu-cuoi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-si