\u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng khi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o vui m\u1eebng h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Barcelona.</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn derby \u0111\u1ea7y cu\u1ed1n h\u00fat</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y ch\u00fa \u00fd: Atletico Madrid m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 5 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu t\u1ea1i La Liga. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Diego Simeone, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Thay v\u00ec khi\u1ebfp s\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Simeone gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i ngang ng\u1eeda th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i khi \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i lo toan cho c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00fd do g\u00ec khi\u1ebfn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-real-madrid-vs-atletico-21h15-ngay-84-la-liga-201718-372-183812.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>tr\u1eadn derby Madrid Real vs Atletico</strong></span> tr\u1edf n\u00ean k\u00e9m h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 m\u00e1u l\u1eeda.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tran derby Madrid Real vs Atletico khong mang niem vui cho ai hinh anh\" title=\"Tr\u1eadn derby Madrid Real vs Atletico kh\u00f4ng mang ni\u1ec1m vui cho ai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Tran-derby-Madrid-Real-vs-Atletico-khong-mang-niem-vui-cho-ai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tr\u1eadn derby Madrid Real vs Atletico di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t gay c\u1ea5n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nY\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 danh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea3 hai th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng khoan nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong t\u1eebng m\u00e9t c\u1ecf. Sau nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Real Madrid 8 ph\u00fat sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hai hi\u1ec7p. T\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u00f3 ngh\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/gareth-bale-roi-real-madrid-ra-yeu-sach-moi-180-183800.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Gareth Bale</strong></span>, CR7 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng pha ch\u1ecdn sai \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Atletico s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Atletico kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tinh th\u1ea7n. C\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 4 ph\u00fat sau, Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ea1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t khi nhanh ch\u00e2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh sau n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c chuy\u1ec1n sang c\u1ee7a Vitolo. 1-1 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn derby Madrid Real vs Atletico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-real-madrid-vs-atletico-21h15-ngay-84-la-liga-201718-372-183812.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/ket-qua-real-madrid-vs-atletico-tran-dau-vong-31-la-liga-201718.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-real-madrid-vs-atletico-21h15-ngay-84-la-liga-201718-372-183812.html\">Real Madrid 1-1 Atletico (KT): Vua derby Ronaldo n\u1ed5 s\u00fang, Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m</span><br>\r\n<span>Real Madrid ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khu\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Atletico tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam qua, khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1, d\u00f9 Ronaldo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 5 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, Real kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Atletico tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, h\u1ecd h\u00f2a c\u0169ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Atletico l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n ngay t\u1ea1i &ldquo;th\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ecba&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Real trong c\u1ea3 3 l\u1ea7n gh\u00e9 th\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby Madrid Real vs Atletico, Ronaldo v\u1eabn bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u00f2n 40 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 sau 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n m\u00f9a n\u00e0y v\u00e0 24 sau 13 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 kh\u00f3 tin v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua tu\u1ed5i 33. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann lai ghi ban truoc Real\" title=\"Griezmann lai ghi ban truoc Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Griezmann-lai-ghi-ban-truoc-Real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Griezmann gi\u00fap Atletico g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 sau 63 ph\u00fat, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ra ngh\u1ec9 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Karim Benzema. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y Zinedine Zidane mu\u1ed1n anh c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League v\u1edbi Juventus, tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng r\u1ee7i ro \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn derby r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThi\u1ebfu Ronaldo, Real c\u0169ng su\u00fdt c\u00f3 b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sergio Ramos may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n. 2 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nguy hi\u1ec3m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y tung ra v\u1edbi 1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t b\u1ecb Jan Oblak c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111i s\u1ea1t khung th\u00e0nh. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu Real c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Atletico, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3 su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ket-qua-real-madrid-vs-atletico-tran-dau-vong-31-la-liga-201718-180-183822.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/ket-qua-real-madrid-vs-atletico-tran-dau-vong-31-la-liga-201718.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ket-qua-real-madrid-vs-atletico-tran-dau-vong-31-la-liga-201718-180-183822.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Real Madrid vs Atletico tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 31 La Liga 2017/18</span><br>\r\n<span>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Real Madrid vs Atletico tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 31 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG T\u00e2y Ban Nha TBN 2017/18 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1,...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng ni\u1ec1m vui thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 k\u1ebb kh\u00e1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ngay c\u1ea3 khi derby Madrid kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1, Atletico v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n vui m\u1eebng. Sau v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 31 c\u1ee7a La Liga, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9m ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barcelona 11 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc 7 tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia (th\u1eafng 24, h\u00f2a 7 sau 31 tr\u1eadn), c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Simeone \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p r\u1ea5t ch\u1eb7t, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 h\u1ecd b\u01b0\u1edbc qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c l\u00ean tr\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Real, ng\u00e0y h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i trao l\u1ea1i ngai v\u00e0ng La Liga c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xa. Los Blancos c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Atletico ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ee9ng n\u00f3i \u0111u\u1ed5i theo ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca v\u1edbi 15 \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real va Atletico deu ko vui\" title=\"Real va Atletico deu ko vui\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Real-va-Atletico-deu-ko-vui.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u1ea3 Real v\u00e0 Atletico \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m vui tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u00e0y, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd cho c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Real h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League v\u1edbi Juventus sau khi \u0111\u00e3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/3-yeu-to-lam-nen-chien-thang-dam-cua-real-truoc-juve-184-183583.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch</strong></span>. Atletico c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sporting Lisbon t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Europa League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 h\u1ea1 Leganes 3-1 v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt (8/4). T\u1edbi bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi 2 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh Madrid \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi khi h\u1ecd c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n nhau 1-1. V\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn derby Madrid Real vs Atletico, chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap b\u1ea1c La Liga ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1eadn c\u1eeda s\u00e2n Camp Nou v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Barca \u0111i v\u00e0i b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n ra \u0111\u00f3n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nReal Madrid: </strong>Keylor; Carvajal, Varane, Ramos, Marcelo; Lucas, Kovacic (Modric 72&rsquo;), Kroos, Asensio (Isco 72&rsquo;); Ronaldo (Benzema 64&rsquo;), Bale.<br>\r\n<strong>Atletico: </strong>Oblak; Juanfran, Savic, God\u00edn, Lucas; Vitolo (Correa 61&rsquo;), Sa\u00fal, Thomas (Gameiro 82&rsquo;), Koke; Griezmann, Diego Costa (Gabi 71&rsquo;).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Real-Madrid-vs-Atletico-Madrid.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid 1-1 Atletico Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid 1-1 Atletico (V\u00f2ng 31 La Liga 2017/18):</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/8/real-1-1-atletico.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-real-madrid-11-atletico-vong-31-la-liga-201718-328-183827.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Real Madrid 1-1 Atletico (V\u00f2ng 31 La Liga 2017/18)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ket-qua-real-madrid-vs-atletico-tran-dau-vong-31-la-liga-201718-180-183822.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Real Madrid vs Atletico tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 31 La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-real-madrid-vs-atletico-21h15-ngay-84-la-liga-201718-372-183812.html\">Real Madrid 1-1 Atletico (KT): Vua derby Ronaldo n\u1ed5 s\u00fang, Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/gerard-pique-phat-bieu-ve-real-va-zidane-180-183807.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Barca m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7 v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-zidane-tu-tin-ve-kha-nang-giu-chan-gareth-bale-180-183743.html\">HLV Zidane t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Gareth Bale</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"941","checkdouble":"183838"},{"date":"09:45 09/04","title":"\"S\u00e1t th\u1ee7 di\u1ec7t Chelsea\" gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ghi b\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/sat-thu-diet-chelsea-giai-thich-nguyen-nhan-khong-ngung-ghi-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-fa