ion:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 33 Premier League, c\u1ef1u sao MU Javier Hernandez \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Chelsea vs West Ham 1-1.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Azpilicueta, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean khi c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd qu\u00e1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Joe Hart, m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng Chelsea vs West Ham 1-1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o ph\u00fat 73, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Chicharito \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, khi\u1ebfn Chelsea m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 Champions League. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 9 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Mexico v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Chelsea, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o anh t\u1eebng ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau 2 th\u00e1ng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o West Ham cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4i m\u00e0, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u. Chicharito l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Chelsea \u00e0? \u1ed2, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00f9a \u0111\u1ea5y!&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u1eefa, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch b\u1edfi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n h\u1ea1 th\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00f4i khi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 duy\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi Chelsea&rdquo; &ndash; C\u1ef1u sao MU ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chicharito g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham 1-1\" title=\"Chicharito g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham 1-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/sat-thu-diet-chelsea-giai-thich-nguyen-nhan-khong-ngung-ghi-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chicharito g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham 1-1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Chelsea hay kh\u00f4ng, b\u1edfi t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch r\u1ed3i (c\u01b0\u1eddi). \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4n kh\u00e9o, t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n m\u1ed9t CLB nh\u01b0 Chelsea.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Arnautovic, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng. Th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y cho West Ham s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Stoke v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, r\u1eddi xa kh\u1ecfi khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng kh\u00e1c trong tr\u1eadn West Ham vs Chelsea 1-1, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Joe Hart c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i Javier Hernandez: &ldquo;Chicha \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau khi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea West Ham vs Chelsea 1-1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/11830326/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">West Ham 1-1 Chelsea<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265880\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/09/highlight-chelsea-vs-west-ham-vong-33-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-chelsea-11-west-ham-top-4-xa-dan-roi-172-183840.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/du-am-chelsea-11-west-ham-top-4-xa-dan-roi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-chelsea-11-west-ham-top-4-xa-dan-roi-172-183840.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Chelsea 1-1 West Ham: Top 4 xa d\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i!</span><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi \u0111\u1ec3 West Ham c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs West Ham khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o Top 4 c\u1ee7a The Blues tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t mong manh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"940","checkdouble":"183859"},{"date":"09:59 09/04","title":"Kane tuy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn Salah trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/13/kane-tuyen-chien-salah-trong-cuoc-dua-vua-pha-luoi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;f