city:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Antonio Rudiger ph\u00ea b\u00ecnh c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tran dau Chelsea vs West Ham Rudiger len mat chi trich dong doi hinh anh\" title=\"Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs West Ham Rudiger l\u00ean m\u1eb7t ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/hoa-dau-west-ham-rudiger-len-mat-chi-trich-dong-doi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Rudiger th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Cesar Azpilicueta \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Chelsea c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. Nh\u01b0ng sang hi\u1ec7p hai, The Blues b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u01a1i ch\u00f9ng xu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 West Ham san b\u1eb1ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Javier Hernandez. Chung cu\u1ed9c, Chelsea b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a ngay t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Conte m\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng khi \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-dong-vien-morata-trong-thoi-khac-gian-kho-172-177565.html\" target=\"_blank\">Rudiger</span> t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f9i d\u1eadp West Ham. Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong hi\u1ec7p hai. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao sau khi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i ch\u00f9ng xu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 trao cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n qu\u00e0. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1ecdt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o top 4. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1eady th\u00f4i&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ngoi-vo-dich-fa-cup-khong-the-thoa-man-muc-tieu-cua-chelsea-172-183853.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/ngoi-vo-dich-fa-cup-khong-the-thoa-man-muc-tieu-cua-chelsea.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ngoi-vo-dich-fa-cup-khong-the-thoa-man-muc-tieu-cua-chelsea-172-183853.html\">Ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\n<span>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Chelsea h\u00f2a West Ham, Cesar Azpilicueta kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi The Blues.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tai h\u1ea1i v\u1eeba qua, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t r\u1ea5t s\u00e2u trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua top 4. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb Tottenham b\u1ecf xa v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a sau. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a The Blues, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang chung tay \u0111\u1ea9y HLV Conte kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. B\u1edfi n\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c, m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong top 4 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi tay <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"bong da 24h\" type=\"bong da 24h\">\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span></span> th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"938","checkdouble":"183861"},{"date":"11:11 09/04","title":"Sanchez n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi Pogba tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn derby?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/sanchez-noi-gi-voi-pogba-truoc-tran-derby.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;displ