e:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Trong cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i \u0103n \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady?</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi b\u1ecb l\u00e9p v\u1ebf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u00e0 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn 2 b\u00e0n, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eebng t\u1ec9nh v\u00ec &ldquo;<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-da-noi-gi-de-giup-mu-nguoc-dong-kinh-dien-truoc-man-city-172-183768.html\" target=\"_blank\">ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u0169 h\u1ec1 nh\u00ecn Man City v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span>&rdquo; &ndash; l\u1eddi Mourinho. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 n\u1eeda sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez &ndash; 2 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong \u0111\u00f3, c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o c\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba, c\u00f9ng 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Alexis Sanchez. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c m\u1edbi cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi xua tan nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn \u1edf trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, khi anh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Sanchez s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Pogba cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft khi anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng, anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00ecn ra kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 lao v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez va Pogba dang co moi quan he rat tot\" title=\"Sanchez v\u00e0 Pogba \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/sanchez-noi-gi-voi-pogba-truoc-tran-derby.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sanchez v\u00e0 Pogba \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1eadt may v\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y t\u00f4i m\u1ecdi l\u00fac: &lsquo;Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu&rsquo;. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, 2 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t hay, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngay t\u1ea1i Etihad. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Manchester-United-1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man United</span> &ndash; \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i 19 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 4-3-3 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford, khi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez. N\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n d\u00e2ng cao khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Nemanja Matic &ndash; Ander Herrera.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/alexis-alejandro-sanchez-43816.html\" target=\"_blank\">Alexis Sanchez</span> c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u01a1n, v\u1edbi tr\u1ea1m trung chuy\u1ec3n Paul Pogba. T\u1eeb gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, c\u00e1c C\u0110V MU r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn derby th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265774\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/08/highlight-man-city-vs-man-utd-vong-33-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/de-tro-thanh-so-1-pogba-can-phai-lam-dieu-nay-172-183814.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1, Pogba c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bi-de-dau-cuoi-co-sao-man-city-khong-phuc-chien-thang-cua-mu-172-183813.html\">B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e8 \u0111\u1ea7u c\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ed5, sao Man City kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-gui-psg-pogba-martial-neymar-172-183797.html\">MU g\u1eedi PSG: Pogba + Martial = Neymar?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-man-city-23-mu-khong-phai-hom-nay-dau-pep-172-183779.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 2-3 MU: Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e2u, Pep!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chung-toi-khong-te-nhu-moi-nguoi-nghi-172-183770.html\">Mourinho: Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-mu-pep-do-loi-cho-hang-thu-172-183791.html\">Thua MU, Pep \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"937","check