ition:-64px -208px}.ui-icon-squaresmall-close{background-position:-80px -208px}.ui-icon-grip-dotted-vertical{background-position:0 -224px}.ui-icon-grip-dotted-horizontal{background-position:-16px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-solid-vertical{background-position:-32px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-solid-horizontal{background-position:-48px -224px}.ui-icon-gripsmall-diagonal-se{background-position:-64px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-diagonal-se{background-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa &ldquo;\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ee5t&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Sanchez, v\u1edbi CLB hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 Man City vs MU 2-3.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2><strong>Qu\u1ea3 cam m\u1ecdng n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a Mourinho<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong> </strong> <br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi&rdquo; &ndash; Mourinho hu\u00eanh hoang, &ldquo;r\u1ea5t th\u00edch \u0103n cam nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u1edf tr\u00ean ng\u1ecdn cao. H\u1ecd t\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u1edf g\u1ea7n v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 cam ngon nh\u1ea5t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Jose Mourinho chia s\u1ebb ngay sau k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/alexis-alejandro-sanchez-43816.html\" target=\"_blank\">bom t\u1ea5n Alexis Sanchez</span> &ndash; m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eabng tay tr\u00ean Man City (v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Chelsea). M\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u00e1p phe kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n ch\u1eb3ng k\u00e9m th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Romelu Lukaku h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, khi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng CLB kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Arsenal, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 2 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ra \u0111i v\u00e0&hellip; chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ra \u0111i. \u1ede m\u00f9a h\u00e8, anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n khi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Man City. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tr\u1ea3i qua n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng kh\u00f4n t\u1ea3, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 d\u1ef1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> tan v\u1ee1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez trong tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU 2-3\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Man City vs MU 2-3 C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Ket-qua-Man-City-vs-MU-2-3-Cau-tra-loi-cua-Alexis-Sanchez-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alexis Sanchez gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng n\u0103m nay, Sanchez c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi CLB tin \u0111\u1ed3n, khi Man xanh \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00f3t tay t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1edbt l\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf &ndash; m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn &ldquo;d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m&rdquo;, c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ngu ng\u1ed1c khi anh ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ec1n thay v\u00ec danh hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1eeb tr\u00e1i tim t\u00f4i, v\u00ec Man United l\u00e0 CLB truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh&rdquo;</strong> &ndash; L\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ai \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Sanchez, khi anh xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng chi\u1ebfc piano trong &ldquo;trailer&rdquo; gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a MU.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pep Guardiola d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i ra, nh\u01b0ng ai c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u \u00f4ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 trong ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 \u0111\u00f4ng, HLV n\u00e0y cu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Riyad Mahrez \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf con c\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i ph\u1ea3i &ldquo;le l\u01b0\u1ee1i&rdquo; khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn l\u1eddi th\u00e1ch gi\u00e1&hellip; 97 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Leicester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, ch\u00ednh Wenger \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f2i Man xanh \u0111\u1ed5i Sanchez l\u1ea5y Sterling. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd x\u1ea3y ra b\u1edfi Man City kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn derby v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Alexis Sanchez g\u00f3p 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, 1 key-pass, c\u00f2n Sterling c\u00f3 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u00f9ng&hellip; 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1ecb b\u1ecf l\u1ee1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t Alexis Sanchez c\u00f2n gi\u1eefa nguy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111ong \u0111\u1ebfm, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 t\u00f4i luy\u1ec7n n\u00ean b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alexis Sanchez derby Manchester Man City vs MU 2-3\" title=\"Alexis Sanchez trong tr\u1eadn derby Manchester Man City vs MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/sanche.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alexis Sanchez lu\u00f4n \u1ea9n ch\u1ee9a tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Khi Pogba \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm ra Sanchez<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong> </strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y g\u00ec khi nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/paul-pogba-44584.html\" target=\"_blank\">Paul Pogba</span>? M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, hay ch\u1ea3i chu\u1ed1t v\u1edbi m\u00e1i t\u00f3c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n? \u0110\u00fang, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. B\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Man City trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, bao g\u1ed3m t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 50 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">97 gi\u00e2y l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa 2 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, k\u00e9o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ea1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Chris Smalling l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. M\u1ed9t minh ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y Paul Pogba ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Man United v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>V\u00e0 anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, khi \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Alexis Sanchez.</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez v\u00e0 Pogba \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y nhau trong tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU\" title=\"Sanchez v\u00e0 Pogba \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/sanchez-noi-gi-voi-pogba-truoc-tran-derby.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sanchez v\u00e0 Pogba \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y nhau trong tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1ee9 ch\u1ea1y \u0111i, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu</strong>&rdquo; &ndash; <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/sanchez-noi-gi-voi-pogba-truoc-tran-derby-172-183865.html\" target=\"_blank\">Pogba ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u1eddi n\u00f3i c\u1ee7a Sanchez</span> v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, v\u00e0 Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n. C\u0169ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1eb3ng k\u00e9m ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, Sanchez c\u0169ng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o trong h\u01a1n 3 n\u0103m (t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 12/2014 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, nh\u01b0ng \u1ea9n ch\u1ee9a hi\u1ec3m h\u1ecda cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1edfi 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, gi\u1eefa v\u00f2ng v\u00e2y h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Man City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Man xanh trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn derby l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 176, Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed3i sinh v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Alexis Sanchez c\u00f9ng Paul Pogba. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, l\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u0169 h\u1ec1 khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m l\u00ean ng\u00f4i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u, Sanchez d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n cho Herrera, b\u00f3ng sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n Pogba v\u00e0 1-2. Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 m\u00e0n ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, khi 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y &ldquo;ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi&rdquo;, ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y c\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Man City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alexis Sanchez l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o trong m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba Man City vs MU\" title=\"Alexis Sanchez l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o trong m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba Man City vs MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/sa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alexis Sanchez l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o trong m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, khi anh \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng. C\u00e1i vung tay c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y trong pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t n\u00f3i l\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u, r\u1eb1ng Sanchez \u0111ang t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i MU. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chris Smalling l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, khi anh tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i lao v\u00e0o h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Ederson, v\u00e0 c\u1ea3&hellip; Vincent Kompany.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o c\u00e1i h\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Pogba cho Sanchez khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y b\u1ecb thay ra, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i. C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi Pogba hay Sanchez quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, th\u1ef1c ra&hellip; ch\u1eb3ng quan tr\u1ecdng. V\u1edbi Mourinho, c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 \u00e1t ch\u1ee7 b\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 &ldquo;truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng g\u00e1nh team&rdquo; nh\u01b0 Sanchez ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn thay \u0111\u1ed5i, ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u00f9i l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Romelu Lukaku, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a CLB, khi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00f9ng chung m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alexis Sanchez v\u00e0 Pogba trong tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU\" title=\"Alexis Sanchez v\u00e0 Pogba Man City vs MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/pogbakisssanchez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Paul Pogba th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez&nbsp; trong tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, Sanchez v\u1eabn b\u1ecb &ldquo;c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t&rdquo; khi t\u1eeb b\u1ecf c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a anh. Th\u1eed ngh\u0129 xem, ai m\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh s\u1eb5n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m Cup, trong khi m\u00ecnh ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m. Anh c\u0169ng g\u1ea1t ngo\u00e0i tai m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean, t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c, v\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5, \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-chung-toi-se-vo-dich-mua-giai-sau-172-183816.html\" target=\"_blank\">ngai v\u00e0ng Premier League </span>\u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City vs MU: 2-3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ghi b\u00e0n<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Man City:</strong> Kompany (25&rsquo;), Gundogan (31&rsquo;)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>MU:</strong> Pogba (53&rsquo;, 55&rsquo;), Smalling (69&rsquo;)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Man City vs MU 2-3</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/11830134/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Man City vs MU<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265774\" style=\"