>Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm v\u00f2ng 32 Serie A, AS Roma \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Fiorentina. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Inter t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua top 4 Serie A.</strong></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Spalletti c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \"qu\u1eb3ng\" n\u00f3 \u0111i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch phung ph\u00ed. Inter ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Torino. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, Nerazzurri v\u1eabn x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 4 \u1edf Serie A nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb v\u0103ng kh\u1ecfi top 4 ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu Lazio gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Udinese.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/9/Torino-1-0-Inter.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Inter ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1. Icardi \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba Perisic, Icardi v\u00e0 Valero. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Rafinha ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n mi\u1ebfng tr\u1ea3 mi\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Ivan Perisic, Candreva (Inter) hay Ljaji\u0107 (Torino) \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat th\u1ee9 19, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Inter l\u1ea1i \u00f4m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Ivan Perisic l\u1ea1i t\u00ecm t\u1edbi tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang. Trong th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng, Torino \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Ph\u00fat 36, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ivan Perisic b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho De Silvestri. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa c\u0103ng ngang cho Ljaji\u0107 s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Inter.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ket qua Torino vs Inter Milan 1-0 tuong thuat Serie A 201718 hinh anh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Torino vs Inter Milan 1-0 t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt Serie A 201718 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/tong-hop-torino-10-inter-milan-vong-31-serie-a-201718.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 42, Ljaji\u0107 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Inter l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf trong th\u1ebf vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7p 2 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng m\u00e3n nh\u00e3n c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Ph\u00fat 57, Ljaji\u0107 b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ea1t c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc khung th\u00e0nh Inter.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00cdt ph\u00fat sau, c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Miranda \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Sirigu nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Torino \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng ngay tr\u00ean v\u1ea1ch v\u00f4i. Sau \u0111\u00f3, HLV Spalletti \u0111\u00e3 tung Rafinha v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Torino.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, Inter chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu \u0111i ch\u00fat may m\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Chung cu\u1ed9c, Inter h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1.</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"935","checkdouble":"183846"},{"date":"06:20 09/04","title":"Napoli 2-1 Chievo: Ki\u00ean tr\u00ec b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/9/napoli-21-chievo-kien-tri-bam-duoi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.