l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i h\u01a1n, Napoli nhanh ch\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 tri\u1ec3n khai c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, Napoli c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 76% v\u00e0 tung ra t\u1edbi 31 c\u00fa s\u00fat, \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0103n b\u00e0n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra do Chievo t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng k\u00edn k\u1ebd. \u0110\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch, lu\u00f4n t\u1eadp trung qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng m\u1ed7i khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9, Napoli ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 sau khi Mertens ng\u00e3 trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11 m, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Sorrentino. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u0169ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n kh\u00e1c khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eadn gi\u1eef qu\u00e1t th\u00e1o b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ket qua Napoli vs Chievo 2-1 tuong thuat Serie A 201718 hinh anh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Napoli vs Chievo 2-1 t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt Serie A 201718 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/20170514-636303796306466181_20170514173112-kAx-U422582063533eED-980x554@MundoDeportivo-Web.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n, Napoli ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n thua \u1edf ph\u00fat 73. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb 1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ebfm hoi c\u1ee7a Chievo, Stepinski tung c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ef1c c\u0103ng v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c v\u00e0o g\u00f3c cao, h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Pepe Reina.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Napoli d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e0ng tr\u00f4i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp. \u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 89, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi v\u00e0o thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Milik \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c, qu\u00e2n b\u00ecnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-1. Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e0 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, ch\u1ec9 3 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, Diawara \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Paolo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSV\u0110 nh\u01b0 n\u1ed5 tung v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Napoli. C\u00f2n 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tham v\u1ecdng l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Juventus. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao khi Bianconeri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"934","checkdouble":"183847"},{"date":"06:24 09/04","title":"Dortmund 3-0 Stuttgart: \u0110\u1ee9ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 tranh ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/9/dortmund-30-stuttgart-dung-len-de-tranh-ngoi-nhi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articl