hi Barca \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leganes tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 th\u00ec Atletico kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Simeone quyet bam duoi Barca du Atletico hoa Real Madrid.\" title=\"Diego Simeone quy\u1ebft b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Barca d\u00f9 Atletico h\u00f2a Real Madrid.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/atletico-hoa-real-madrid-diego-simeone-gui-loi-de-doa-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Diego Simeone quy\u1ebft b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Barca d\u00f9 Atletico h\u00f2a Real Madrid.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Atletico c\u00f2n b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/cristiano-ronaldo-44953.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Cristiano Ronaldo</span></span>. \u0110\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch gi\u00e0nh 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n coi tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng La Liga khi HLV Zidane r\u00fat Ronaldo ra ngh\u1ec9 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>L\u1eddi \u0111e d\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Simeone</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Barca b\u1ecb n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng khi Atletico h\u00f2a Real Madrid, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/huan-luyen-vien/diego-simeone-38.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Diego Simeone</span> kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1edd tr\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga: &quot;T\u00f4i mong \u0111\u1ee3i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga, hy v\u1ecdng \u1edf ba tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u1edf trong th\u1ebf c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Real Madrid \u01b0? \u01afu ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Champions League, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua, c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 nh\u01b0 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ed9 l\u00ean th\u00f4ng tin HLV Diego Simeone c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Atletico Madrid trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 t\u00f2 m\u00f2 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, &quot;El Cholo&quot; ch\u1ec9 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn: &quot;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng La Liga, theo ghi nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn, Atletico Madrid c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League. Atletico \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sporting CP v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Real-Madrid-vs-Atletico-Madrid.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p Real Madrid 1-1 Atletico:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/8/real-1-1-atletico.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nN.D (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"930","checkdouble":"183851"},{"date":"02:38 09/04","title":"Ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m Chelsea 1-1 West Ham: M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Joe Hart","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/cham-diem-chelsea-11-west-ham.JPG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(Not