0eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda The Blues.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cham diem Chelsea vs West Ham - Vong 33 Ngoai hang Anh hinh anh\" title=\"Ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m Chelsea vs West Ham - V\u00f2ng 33 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Cham-diem-Chelsea-vs-West-Ham---Vong-33-Ngoai-hang-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m Chelsea vs West Ham vinh danh Joe Hart&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nEden Hazard, Marcos Alonso hay Giroud \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c, song \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ch\u1eb7n l\u1ea1i. Ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m Chelsea vs West Ham vinh danh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Joe Hart, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Daily Mail ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1edbi 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean ph\u00eda West Ham, Chicharito, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m 7, c\u00f9ng nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m 7 l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Rice. S\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5m ch\u1ec9 thua duy nh\u1ea5t Joe Hart.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Fernandes b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda West Ham, anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5m 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Chicharito.</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard v\u00e0 Willian x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/thong-ke-chelsea-11-west-ham-172-183835.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Chelsea vs West Ham </strong></span>l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Cahill v\u00e0 Moses, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5m 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m, s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda The Blues. Hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian la cai ten choi noi bat trong hiep mot tran Chelsea vs West Ham.\" title=\"Willian l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/willian.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i West Ham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/eden-hazard-44350.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Hazard</strong></span> l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Chelsea v\u1edbi 7.5 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Willian v\u00e0 Kante x\u1ebfp sau v\u1edbi 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAzpilicueta, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/chelsea-6.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Chelsea</strong></span> ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5m 6.5 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nh\u00ecn chung ngo\u00e0i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 th\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-chelsea-11-west-ham-172-183837.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn Chelsea 1-1 West Ham</strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chelsea 3-4-3: </strong>Courtois 6; Azpilicueta 6.5, Cahill 5, Rudiger 6; Moses 5 (Pedro 78&rsquo;, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m), Fabregas 6, Kante 7, Alonso 6; Willian 7, Morata 6 (Giroud 78&rsquo;, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m), Hazard 7.5</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>West Ham 3-4-3:</strong> Hart 8; Rice 7, Ogbonna 6, Cresswell 6 (Evra 63&rsquo;, 6); Zabaleta 6, Kouyate 6, Noble 6, Masuaku 6.5; Fernandes 5 (Chicharito 70&rsquo;, 7), Arnautovic 6, Mario 6 (Cullen 84&rsquo;, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"929","checkdouble":"183836"},{"date":"01:28 09/04","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea 1-1 West Ham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-chelsea-11-west-ham.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate2>a:h