2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a David Moyes ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV David Moyes \u1edf tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Trong th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n, ph\u00fat 70 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 54 tu\u1ed5i tung Chicharito v\u00e0o thay Edimilson Fernandes, ch\u1ec9 3 ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, Moyes \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Josh Cullen v\u00e0 Patrice Evra v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gi\u00fap West Ham r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung diem nhan sau tran Chelsea vs West Ham hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-Chelsea-vs-West-Ham-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chicharito ghi b\u00e0n sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 ph\u00fat</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a HLV Conte kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng. Giroud v\u00e0o s\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong kho\u1ea3ng 20 ph\u00fat tr\u00ean s\u00e2n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ecb Joe Hart c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. Pedro g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Conte t\u1ecf ra thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi David Moyes.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa Alvaro Morata v\u00e0 Cesar Azpilicueta l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng nhau t\u1ea1o ra b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi West Ham, Morata \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. Morata ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, sau khi ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi Leicester v\u00e0 Tottenham, anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Azpilicueta ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata va Azpilicueta khong the giup Chelsea gianh 3 diem\" title=\"Morata v\u00e0 Azpilicueta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/cueta.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata v\u00e0 Azpilicueta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nV\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Azpilicueta, anh \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 9 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i Premier League cho Chelsea t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, bao g\u1ed3m ghi 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 6. B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ea1o ra b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c n\u00e0o l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n (b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Salah &ndash; Firmino v\u00e0 Salah &ndash; Mane).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa Morata v\u00e0 Azpilicueta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Joe Hart</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">West Ham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu t\u1edbi 23 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 6 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, song h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Joe Hart c\u1ea3n l\u1ea1i. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Cesar Azpilicueta \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n, song Hart v\u1eabn x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joe Hart choi an tuong tren san cua Chelsea\" title=\"Joe Hart ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Joe Hart ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n c\u1ee9u thua tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ef1c kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Hazard, Marcos Alonso hay Giroud. Hart v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap West Ham c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Willian</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Willian kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham, nh\u01b0ng anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/chelsea-6.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Chelsea</strong></span> ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9, anh l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5, t\u1eeb t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 tham gia h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian la cai ten choi noi bat trong hiep mot tran Chelsea vs West Ham.\" title=\"Willian l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/willian.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian ch\u01a1i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nWillian c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Hazard l\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1edbi 5 l\u1ea7n, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Joe Hart khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, anh 6 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o t\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n, song&nbsp;Hazard hay Alonso \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Conte \u0111ang b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 &ldquo;\u0111\u00e2m sau l\u01b0ng&rdquo;, nh\u01b0ng Willian kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3. Anh v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u00f9 t\u1eebng b\u1ecb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia gh\u1ebb l\u1ea1nh \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Willian l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Chelsea g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o Top 4</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Stoke City, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa Chelsea v\u00e0 Spurs \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 11 \u0111i\u1ec3m. The Blues bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i West Ham n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Top 4. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Azpilicueta, nh\u01b0ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Chicharito khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea da kem Top 4 den 10 diem\" title=\"Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9m Top 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/chelsea.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9m Top 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nKho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Top 4 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 5 v\u00f2ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1edf m\u1ed9t trong b\u1ed1n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd n\u00ean chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Europa League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai HLV Conte th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-chelsea-vs-west-ham-tran-dau-vong-33-premier-league-201718-172-183823.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea vs West Ham</span>, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ee9c ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn c\u1ee7a t\u1ef7 ph\u00fa ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea1n ki\u1ec7t. N\u1ebfu trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs West Ham<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Chelsea vs West Ham\" title=\